content.rendered:
Now in Telugu

The power to do anything you want resides only within you. Be A Winner urges you to make use of it and be everything you have ever wanted to be.

The author, Norman Vincent Peale, has outlined in this book, methods of living and attitudes of mind that you can follow to win over any obstacle that may come your way in life. It highlights all the possible sources of your spiritual and personal power and tells you how you can use them to your best possible advantage.
